text: Joanie Gillingham (born 21 February 1961) is a Canadian rower. She competed in the women's eight event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Canadian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Canada Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:People from Twentynine Palms, California
